data.description: Back on the market due to no fault of seller. Quaint ranch nestled in the heart of old Pooler. This charming home boasts 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. As you enter, you'll be greeted by vaulted ceilings in the living room, a formal dining area, and a chef's kitchen complete with ample cabinet and counter space, along with a full set of appliances. Step outside to unwind in the large backyard surrounded by pine trees, offering a serene atmosphere. Convenient amenities include a garage and storage shed for all your belongings. NO HOA!! Don't miss the opportunity to schedule a private tour today!
